CatDescriptText: The banner overhead in the background reads, "...Of The 78th Annual Session of the Pittsburgh A.M.E Conference Sept. 19th Through 23, 1945 The Rt. Rev. R.C. Ransom Presiding Bishop The Rt. Rev. F.M. Reid Associate Bishop Rev. John D. Bright Minister".
